videos.headline: Taylor bulldozes way to Wisconsin TD
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor plows his way through the Rutgers defense for a 5-yard Wisconsin touchdown.

videos.headline: Hornibrook throws first INT of day
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook's deep pass is picked off by Rutgers defender Saquan Hampton.

videos.headline: Hornibrook picked off for second time by Hampton
videos.description: Saquan Hampton comes up with his second interception of the day for Rutgers on another Alex Hornibrook pass.

videos.headline: Wisconsin blocks Rutgers' FG attempt
videos.description: Wisconsin hustles to block Rutgers' field goal attempt and D'Cota Dixon returns it 34 yards for the Badgers.

videos.headline: Taylor takes off for 38-yard Wisconsin TD
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor burst through Rutgers' defense to score a 38-yard touchdown, putting the Badgers up 17-0.

videos.headline: Taylor goes 18 yards for third TD vs. Rutgers
videos.description: Wisconsin's Jonathan Taylor navigates his way through the Rutgers defense for an 18-yard touchdown, his third rushing TD of the game.

videos.headline: Rutgers' Hilliman scores TD
videos.description: Jonathan Hilliman scores Rutgers' first touchdown of the day by powering through the Wisconsin defense at the goal line.

videos.headline: Sitkowski connects with Blackshear for 5-yard Rutgers TD
videos.description: Rutgers' Artur Sitkowski throws his first touchdown pass of the day to Raheem Blackshear.
